{"name":"Fire Knuckle","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact firearm affixed to a gauntlet, combining close-quarters striking power with a short-range shot.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Melee d6, Ranged d4+5 (10/20), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Clockwork, Hipshot, Steady, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":750,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":20,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fir","rel"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you hit with a melee attack, the next ranged attack made this turn with this weapon against the same creature has advantage and counts as a critical hit."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Arquebus","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-musket-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long, heavy two-handed firearm capable of devastating ranged fire and fitted with a bayonet for close combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 2d10+5 (300/900), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Sighted</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":500,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":10,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":10,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"+5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":300,"long":900,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can arm the bayonet with an object interaction and the arquebus gains Brace, Double Ended d6, Finesse, Reach."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Blunderbuss","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-blunderbuss-bronze.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A wide-mouthed, short-ranged firearm that unleashes a devastating spread of shot, capable of knocking enemies off their feet.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Ranged 2d8+5 (40/60), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Knockback, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":300,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"+5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On hit, a target within 15 ft must succeed on a Strength saving throw or becomes your choice of pushed back 5ft or prone."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Firelance","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-musket-brown.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A polearm-mounted firearm that can both stab in melee and unleash a cone of fire at close range.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Melee d12, Ranged d10 (15 ft cone), Reload (bonus action), Firearm</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":200,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["piercing","fire"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":15,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","fir","rel"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action, you sweep the lance around you, forcing all creatures within 10 ft to succeed on a Dexterity saving throw or become blinded until the end of their next turn. The weapon must be loaded to use this action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Gunblade","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A hybrid weapon combining a blade with a built-in firearm, allowing seamless transitions between melee and ranged combat.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Melee d8, Ranged 2d6+5 (40/160), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Hipshot, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":350,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing","slashing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":40,"long":160,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can make one additional attack as part of your Attack action. If you made a ranged attack with this weapon, then this additional attack must be a melee attack. If you made a melee attack with this weapon, then this additional attack must be a ranged attack."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Hand Cannon","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy one-handed firearm delivering powerful shots at range with good accuracy.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Ranged 2d6+5 (80/320), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Hipshot, Puncture, Sighted, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":250,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"+5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":80,"long":320,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As a bonus action, you can make an attack with this weapon if you haven't used the attack action or held your action."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Pepperbox","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A compact multi-barreled firearm that can be easily concealed and fires multiple shots in rapid succession.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Ranged d4+5 (30/120), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Conceal, Hipshot</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":1000,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":"+5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt","fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"As an action you fire all barrels at once, ignoring Reload and rolling an attack for each loaded barrel. The weapon is destroyed if you roll a 1, but could be repaired with smith's tools."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Portable Cannon","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-blunderbuss-bronze.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive shoulder-mounted cannon capable of devastating long-range bombardment, staggering and sundering armor on impact.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Ranged 3d10+5 (200/800), Reload (action), Firearm</td><td>Knockback, Sighted, Stagger, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":750,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":12,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":3,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":"+5"},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":200,"long":800,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can choose to overpack your weapon when you Reload, spending three uses of gunpowder. When you fire the cannon, all creatures in a 15ft cone must succeed on a Constitution saving throw or be blinded and deafened until the start of their next turn. If you roll a 1 on your attack roll when you overpack, the cannon is destroyed but could be repaired later with smith's tools."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Wrist Rocket","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A clockwork firearm strapped to the wrist, easily concealed and triggered with a nimble flick for surprise fire.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Affixed, Ranged 2d4 (range varies), Reload (attack), Firearm</td><td>Clockwork, Conceal, Hipshot, Nimble, Steady</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":150,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["fire"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":30,"long":120,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialR","baseItem":""},"properties":["fir","rel","amm"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Firearms","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If an enemy you can see misses you with an attack, you can use your reaction to make an attack against that enemy."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Claw Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A light flail tipped with hooked claws, capable of entangling and wounding enemies with quick, nimble strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Clockwork, Entangle, Nimble, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":35,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["slashing","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you land an attack using your Conceal property, the enemy cannot make a saving throw against your entangle attack, and suffers disadvantage on its saving throw against any other use of your Weapon DC."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Double Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy flail with spiked heads on both ends, designed to batter through defenses and punish enemies even on disadvantaged swings.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d4, Versatile 2d6</td><td>Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":7,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","ver"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you suffer disadvantage but one dice would have hit, you deal 1 of the weapon's damage dice plus your Strength modifier, even though this still counts as a miss. If you have advantage and both dice hit, add your Strength modifier twice to the damage total."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Great Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive two-handed flail with reach, capable of knocking back enemies and even sundering their shields.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee d12, Reach</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Reach, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":12,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":12,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can attack an adjacent target if your attack misses the first target. If the enemy is wielding a shield, your successful sunder disarms them of it, in addition to lowering AC."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Heavy Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A reliable one-handed flail that can be used two-handed for greater damage, with entangling and punching capabilities.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d8, Versatile d10</td><td>Entangle, Punch, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":5,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy","ver"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If your target successfully saves against your weapon DC, you can make a weapon attack as part of the same action. This additional attack must be a normal weapon attack, and cannot be a property attack forcing another saving throw."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Light Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A quick, light flail suited for disarming and tripping opponents with agile, one-handed strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Disarm, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":8,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can reroll any attack you miss, but must take the new result."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Nunchaku","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A pair of handles connected by a short chain, wielded with finesse to conceal, entangle, and trip opponents.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4</td><td>Conceal, Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can use the Double Ended property one-handed. Dual wielding two nunchaku, you can attack twice with Double Ended."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Pole Flail","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long-hafted flail with reach, capable of entangling and knocking back enemies while preventing opportunity attacks.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee d10</td><td>Entangle, Knockback, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":10,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you make a melee attack against a creature, you don't provoke opportunity attacks from that creature for the rest of the turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Rope Hammer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A weighted hammer on a rope, used with finesse to entangle and trip foes, and to deflect incoming strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d6</td><td>Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":1,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you roll a Deflect roll, you can make an attack as part of the same reaction."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Spring Mace","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A clockwork mace with an extending spring mechanism that grants surprising reach and a powerful first strike with knockback.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Reach, Melee d8</td><td>Clockwork, Knockback, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":75,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"The first time during an encounter you use Reach or Lunge with this weapon, your attack gains advantage. If this attack hits, it deals weapon damage and your enemy must make a saving throw with disadvantage against the Knockback property."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Trisectional Staff","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-ball-chain-grey.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A three-section staff with flexible joints, granting finesse and reach while entangling and tripping enemies.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Finesse, Reach, Melee d6, Double Ended d4</td><td>Entangle, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","fin","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Flails","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your Disarm, Entangle, and Trip attacks can deal bludgeoning damage equal to your Dexterity modifier, instead of Strength."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Great Pick","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A massive two-handed war pick designed to punch through armor, barb into flesh, and inflict grievous wounds.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6</td><td>Barbed, Entangle, Puncture, Punch, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":6,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your Wound property uses 2d8 instead of a single d8 weapon damage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Light Hammer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-light-blue.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small, throwable hammer suitable for quick strikes in melee or at range, delivering punishing blows.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d6, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Punch</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"simpleM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you score a mighty blow, your enemy suffers a d4 penalty to their next Strength, Dexterity, or Wisdom saving throw. When you score a critical hit, the enemy suffers a d6 penalty to their next saving throw of any ability."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Light Pick","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A small, light pick that can be thrown, used to pierce, slip past defenses, and trip enemies with quick finesse attacks.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Slip, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":2,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"Your piercing damage perk gains +2 to attack, rather than +1."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Lucerne","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A long polearm combining hammer and pick heads, with reach for bracing against charges and sundering armor.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Reach, Melee 2d6</td><td>Brace, Punch, Puncture, Sunder, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":25,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":8,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy","rch"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If your enemy succeeds on the save from your Sunder, they instead take normal weapon damage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Maul","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A great two-handed war hammer that sends enemies flying with devastating knockback and staggering force.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>Two-Handed, Heavy, Melee 2d6</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Stagger, Trip</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":10,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":12,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":2,"denomination":6,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["two","hvy"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"On hit, you can move a same size or smaller enemy 5ft, and your Knockback moves 10ft. You count as one size category larger for Knockback."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Stiletto","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A slender, easily concealed piercing weapon designed to punch through gaps in armor with precise, deadly thrusts.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Finesse, Light, Melee d4</td><td>Conceal, Punch, Puncture</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":5,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["fin","lgt"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"You can use a bonus action to attempt to shove a creature you are entangling."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"Wall Pick","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A light pick designed to hook into surfaces and enemies alike, entangling and wounding foes with barbed strikes.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Light, Melee d4, Thrown (20/60)</td><td>Barbed, Entangle, Punch, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":3,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":1,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":4,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["lgt","thr"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If your Entangle misses, you can reroll the attack but must take the new roll. If you score a powerful blow, your enemy is restrained and grappled."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Hammer","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A versatile war hammer that can be used one- or two-handed, capable of punishing blows, staggering, and sundering armor.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8, Versatile d10</td><td>Punch, Stagger, Sunder</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":3,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning","piercing"],"bonus":""}},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["ver"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"If you move at least 10 ft in a straight line before your attack, your Sunder can lower an enemy's AC by -2 with one hand, or -3 with two hands."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Mallet","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/hammers/hammer-war-metal.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A heavy one-handed mallet that delivers crushing knockback and staggering blows, overwhelming enemies when wielded with advantage.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Heavy, Melee d10</td><td>Knockback, Punch, Stagger</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":20,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":4,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":10,"types":["bludgeoning"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":["hvy"],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you have advantage, the saves to resist your weapon DC are made with disadvantage."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
{"name":"War Pick","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/polearms/pick-war-steel.webp","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>A one-handed war pick that punctures armor, wounds, and trips enemies, with a unique escalating bleed wound mechanic.</p><table><thead><tr><th>Training</th><th>Properties</th><th>Special</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Basic</td><td>One-Handed, Melee d8</td><td>Punch, Puncture, Sunder, Trip, Wound</td></tr></tbody></table>"},"price":{"value":15,"denomination":"gp"},"weight":{"value":2,"units":"lb"},"damage":{"base":{"number":1,"denomination":8,"types":["piercing"],"bonus":""},"versatile":null},"range":{"value":5,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"type":{"value":"martialM","baseItem":""},"properties":[],"equipped":false},"effects":[],"flags":{"rnk-commanders-rme":{"rmeData":{"group":"Hammers & Picks","trainingLevel":"basic","masterPerk":"When you Wound, roll a d10. The enemy takes that damage instead of the normal Wound mechanics, and each round after that, it takes 1 fewer damage. You can refresh this Wound with a higher roll than the damage the enemy took on its previous turn."}}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"5.2.5"}}
